Metacells data

Source: R/data.R
metacells_data.Rd

A gene expression matrix corresponding to the single cell object, in this case it corresponds to the reduced single cell object (metacells), not the original.

Usage

metacells_data

Format

Matrix with samples as columns and genes names (SYMBOL) as rows

Source

Senosain et al. (2023), doi: 10.1158/2767-9764.CRC-22-0373. PMID: 37501683; PMCID: PMC10370362

Examples

data(metacells_data)
